  - if false
    .page-box.myapnea-white-bg.d-flex.align-items-center
      .container
        =# .myapnea-light-bg
        .mb-3
          .landing-blog-title.text-dark
            What is MyApnea?

          .landing-blog-content
            MyApnea is a patient-powered community that empowers patients to learn about
            sleep apnea and contribute to sleep apnea research.

        .mb-3
          .landing-blog-title.text-dark
            What you can do on MyApnea

          .landing-blog-content
            %p
              Share your story on MyApnea, fill out sleep related surveys.

            %p
              Engage with other patients and professionals on the forum to discuss
              anything and everything related to sleep apnea.

            %p
              Give back to research by completing ongoing research surveys.


        .mb-3
          .landing-blog-title.text-dark
            What you can expect from MyApnea

          .landing-blog-content
            %p
              Surveys you complete will provide you feedback on how you relate to others
              on MyApnea that have participated in the survey.

            %p
              MyApnea will publish articles relating to sleep apnea news, research, and
              patient experiences with sleep apnea.

            %p
              MyApnea provides a safe and engaging forum to learn and ask questions to fellow MyApnea members.
